85c15d8c-f018-46cb-b09b-049699c91377.title: Murphy
85c15d8c-f018-46cb-b09b-049699c91377.text:
Getting ready to go fishing of course. There's no time
to waste!

5be292ac-5f3b-4508-827a-9c18561c918f.title: Murphy
5be292ac-5f3b-4508-827a-9c18561c918f.text:
I've got all the supplies I need from the shop at the end
of the pier. They sell good rope, hammers and axes
although their bailing buckets aren't too effective.

options.text: Your boat doesn't look too safe.

b95f9918-055b-48bd-84b9-a98c9a290362.title: Murphy
b95f9918-055b-48bd-84b9-a98c9a290362.text:
I get all sorts, anything that lies on the sea bed, you
never know what you're going to get until you pull up
the net!

options.text: Your boat doesn't look too safe.

72da093f-35de-4d3d-b237-2d6bec3991cf.title: <player>
72da093f-35de-4d3d-b237-2d6bec3991cf.text: Your boat doesn't look too safe.

c4e002c4-1fcb-4801-b198-6356060649d9.title: Murphy
c4e002c4-1fcb-4801-b198-6356060649d9.text: That's because it's not, the darn thing's full of holes.

c8ef4f95-733a-4a78-b4e4-277ab81df27b.title: <player>
c8ef4f95-733a-4a78-b4e4-277ab81df27b.text: Oh, so I suppose you can't go out for a while?

0bdc70a5-695d-4819-8fd9-7746462f53f7.title: Murphy
0bdc70a5-695d-4819-8fd9-7746462f53f7.text:
Oh no, I don't let a few holes stop an experienced sailor
like me. I could sail these seas in a barrel, I'll be going
out soon enough.

35204c60-3953-4323-9493-18e27148303a.title: Murphy
35204c60-3953-4323-9493-18e27148303a.text:
Well of course you can! I'll warn you though, the seas
are merciless and without fishing experience you won't
catch much.

238c4172-6af5-4f22-a355-900bcbe1fc29.title: Murphy
238c4172-6af5-4f22-a355-900bcbe1fc29.text:
You need a fishing level of 15 or above to catch any
fish on the trawler.

ba226ab3-51a8-4c54-87fd-0c230efae356.title: Murphy
ba226ab3-51a8-4c54-87fd-0c230efae356.text:
On occasions the net rips, so you'll need some rope to
repair it.

639d67d0-8f7c-4e82-9920-502926261980.title: Murphy
639d67d0-8f7c-4e82-9920-502926261980.text:
Repairing the net is difficult in the harsh conditions so
you'll find it easier with a higher crafting level.

5a928533-2908-4ba2-911d-8d10068d51aa.title: Murphy
5a928533-2908-4ba2-911d-8d10068d51aa.text: There's also a slight problem with leaks.

b2783632-a7fd-4647-a553-c0992cccb8a2.title: Murphy
b2783632-a7fd-4647-a553-c0992cccb8a2.text: Nothing some swamp paste won't fix...

33c18796-44cc-4855-973b-48490f6dabec.title: Murphy
33c18796-44cc-4855-973b-48490f6dabec.text: Also, there's the small matter of the Kraken.

e80fcc9c-3193-416e-82c0-267de71a6baa.title: <player>
e80fcc9c-3193-416e-82c0-267de71a6baa.text: You have got to be kidding me?

8c8e6037-f7b2-42ce-9ba6-2975813a3b60.title: Murphy
8c8e6037-f7b2-42ce-9ba6-2975813a3b60.text:
Occupational hazard. I usually whack it with an axe a
few time and fix the damage with hammer once it's
gone.

f1dc6a95-9b26-4224-afad-b00e60f8002b.title: Murphy
f1dc6a95-9b26-4224-afad-b00e60f8002b.text:
Oh, and one more thing... I hope you're a good
swimmer?

options.text: Actually, I think I'll leave it.

6b9fec5d-b534-4d90-84e4-02a2b1e265a1.title: Murphy
6b9fec5d-b534-4d90-84e4-02a2b1e265a1.text:
Swamp tar mixed with flour which is then heated over a
fire.

18878e69-6986-45a4-85b5-3f79910166b1.title: <player>
18878e69-6986-45a4-85b5-3f79910166b1.text: Where can I find swamp tar?

d92023a9-4bd0-4e36-a959-98f948178ffb.title: Murphy
d92023a9-4bd0-4e36-a959-98f948178ffb.text:
Unfortunately the only supply of swamp tar is in the
swamps below Lumbridge.

fc44865c-b0e0-4fde-817b-aa4acd264425.title: <player>
fc44865c-b0e0-4fde-817b-aa4acd264425.text: Actually, I think I'll leave it.

6aeaa288-ead5-4429-b50d-0e9794bca507.title: Murphy
6aeaa288-ead5-4429-b50d-0e9794bca507.text:
Aye aye! Meet me on board the trawler. I just need to
get a few things together.
